 The Hellions  and the SA Paintball GameDay Porta Pottys are on site

***UPDATED EVENT ITINERARY***

10:00am - 10:15am: Welcoming, Rules & Regulations, General Event Information.

10:30am – 11:10am: “The Guardians” (1st Point Based Game, 40 Minutes). Head Shots To Eliminate All Guardians On Both Sides, Must Take Out All Guardians Or Have More Eliminated Within The Scheduled Time Frame. Unlimited Respawns For All Players. All Non-Guardians Must Step Inside Orange Respawn Ring & Can Return To Battle. If There’s A Tie 3-vs-3 Guardians Will Battle To Determine Who Wins, 5 Minute Game. Guardians Must Remain At All Times Within The Kill Zone, Which Will Be Visibly Displayed By Colored Tape On Both Sides Of The Fence Post.
  
11:20am – 11:40am: Break, Prize Giveaways, Announcement, Etc.

11:50pm – 12:30pm: Slap-Stick Domination, *Landscape Battle* (2nd Point Based Game, 40 Minutes). Head & Torso Shots Only For All Players, Unlimited Repsawns, Will Need To Touch Any Part Of The Fence Post. Once We Reach The Last 10 Minutes Of The Game, All Players Eliminated Can No Longer Return In The Game. At The End Of The Game, Whichever Team Has All 3 Or The Majority Of Their Slap Stick Colors In The Upright Position Wins.
   
12:40pm – 1:10pm: Break, Prize Giveaways, Music & Sponsor Recognition's.

1:20pm – 1:50pm: “300 Battle” Part 3 (1st Cos Play Match, 30 Minutes). 40 Spartans W/ Shields Must Defend The Alamo For 30 Minutes, Persians Are Eliminated With 1 Shot Anywhere To The Body, Unlimited Respawns For All Persians Until The 20 Minute Mark At Which There Are No More Respawns. Spartans Are Eliminated W/ 1 Head Shot Only Or Upon Giving Up. No Respawns For Spartans. Game Is Over When All The Spartans Are Eliminated Or The Time Limit Is Up. If 1 Spartan Remains, By Game Rule Default, The Spartans Win.

2:00pm – 2:45pm: Intermission, Ticket Drawing, Music & Games, Free Play, Speedball Challenge, Gauntlet Run, (All Courses Will Be Available For 45 Minutes Of Free Play).
 
3:00pm – 3:30pm: FINAL BATTLE/FORT SHOWDOWN, (3rd Point Based Game, 40 Minutes). All Shots Count As An Elimination, Markers Hits Do Not Count, Unlimited Respawns, Each Team Will Begin At Their Designated Starting Points. One Player From Each Team Will Begin In The Fort, At The Sound Of The Horn Both Players Will Run To His Teams Location, Once They’ve Arrived All Players On Both Sides Can Begin To Move About The Field With The Objective To Hold The Fort. The Objective For One Team To Secure & Defend The Fort Till The End Of The Game. The Game Winning Point Will Be Determined By The Team That Has Their Center Slap Stick Color Displayed In The Upright Position.
   
3:40pm – 3:55pm: Break, Last Prize Giveaways, Dance Contest & Closing Announcements.

4:10pm - 4:40pm: Zombie Apocalypse Survivor (2nd Cos Play Match, 30 Minutes). Players Will Be Issued A Piece Of White Tape To Be Visibly Worn On Their Mask. All Humans Will Be Given 10 Minutes To Spread Out All Over The Field. At The Sound Of The Horn All 10 Zombies Will Be Unleashed To Infect All Humans. Once Released Zombies Can Shot Any Human, 1 Hit Anywhere From A Zombie On Any Part Of The Body & The Human Is Now Infected As A Zombie. That Human Must Take Off His Tape Off To Be Identified As A Zombie, Toss It On The Ground & Proceed To Infect More Humans. Zombies Must Attack & Eliminate Every Human Player Until Only 1 Human Remains, All Zombies Can Be Eliminated By A Single Head Shot ONLY. There Are No Respawns For Zombies.

5:00pm – 6:00pm: Free Play Paintball, Closing.
